== Missions ==

Missions are the primary source of TRP, Accolades, and MRP in Talsia. They are accepted at the Mission Briefing in either Delta or Alpha Sector. Each mission completion awards a base amount of TRP and Accolades, plus converts accumulated MRP into experience and credits.

'''Mission Reward Points (MRP)''' are earned during patrol from battles, bunkers, relay stations, and other encounters. At mission completion, all accumulated MRP are converted into experience and credits. The conversion rate scales with TRP (up to the 18,000 TRP cap) and BM (up to ~14M BM).

