| '''Order of the CyLegion''' || 90%+ mission success rate with 150+ completed missions || Merit bar + [[Y-Link]] upgraded to '''[[MKII Y-Bot]]''' ([[Tribolt Hydron]] reactor, 3,000 energy, 2x [[Plasma Beam]], 108 speed)
|-
| '''Master of Talsia''' || Complete 200 missions with 90%+ success rate || Merit bar + access to '''[[Advanced Master Fire Director]] (AMFD)''' module
|}

'''Notes on awards:'''
* The '''[[Pneumatron Reactor]]''' (Star of Talsia) is one of the most valuable rewards — its 10,000 energy makes the [[CySentinel]] virtually immune to energy drain
* The '''[[Rayden Device]]''' (Union of Service) is a powerful draining super weapon; equip on [[Leviathan]] for maximum drain output
* The '''[[Advanced Master Fire Director|AMFD]]''' (Master of Talsia) is the endgame module for maximising fire rate and critical hit chance on [[Seer|Seers]]
* The '''[[Leviathan]]''' (Order of the Regiment) is the first super-chassis available in Talsia; ensure workshop space before claiming
* The '''[[Y-Link]]''' module (CyCorps Commendation) provides an orbital strike bot that fires automatically each turn

