== Typical Enemy Compositions ==

The following are representative enemy squad compositions encountered in Talsia at high BM (~30M):

'''Infantry squads:'''
* 4–5x Heavy Infantry, 3–6x Siege Blaster Squad, 2–5x Heavy Shield Projector, 2–4x Grenadiers, 1–2x Lieutenant

'''Tank squads (common):'''
* 6–8x Main Battle Tank, 2x C6II Enertron, 1–2x Ae7 Barrier Tank, 1–2x Amplifier Tank, 1–2x Command Tank, 1–2x Syncron Tank, 1–2x Heavy Siege Tank

'''Tank squads (shield-heavy):'''
* 2–4x Syncron Tank, 2–3x Ae7 Barrier Tank, 2–3x Main Battle Tank

'''Bombardier squads:'''
* 4x Bombardier, 2x Heavy Infantry, 4x Heavy Shield Projector, 1x Lieutenant

'''Guerrilla/Recon squads:'''
* 10x Carrion, 5x Heavy Reconoiter

'''TRAF Round 1:'''
* 2x Uplink Command, 10x PR600 Launcher

'''TRAF Round 2:'''
* 1x Reinforced Wall, 8x Rhino, 3x Uplink Command, 3x SR180 Receptor

'''TRAF Round 3:'''
* 1x Reinforced Wall, 6x Rhino, 3–4x Heavy Siege Tank, 2x Uplink Command, 4x SR180 Receptor

'''TRAF Round 4 (True Guard):'''
* 3x True Guard Shielding, 5x Manium Firespray, 3x Cortex Tank, 3x True Guard, 4x Storm Bringer, 2x SR180 Receptor

'''Warship (Destroyer):'''
* 12x Heavy Gun Turret, 1x Bridge, 1x Destroyer Hull, 2x Shield Generator

'''Warship (Cruiser):'''
* 3x Devastator Battery, 1x Bridge, 5x Heavy Gun Turret, 1x Cruiser Hull, 6x Shield Generator

